# Retail Sales Analysis - Exploratory Data Analysis (EDA)

## Introduction

This project, undertaken as part of Oasis Infobyte's data science initiatives, focuses on conducting a comprehensive Exploratory Data Analysis (EDA) on retail sales data. By examining various aspects of the sales data, including customer behavior, product performance, and seasonal trends, the project aims to derive actionable insights to inform business strategies and improve operational efficiency.

